# @desc   Tap the submit button on the IOU confirmation page (IOURequestStepConfirmation). Triggers ManualCreateExpenseSubmit, ManualSubmitToDestinationVisible, and ManualCreateExpenseServerResponse. If the device has location permission granted, ManualGeolocationWait also fires as a child of Submit. Requires being on the confirmation page already.
# @pre    role="button" label="Upload receipt"
# @pre    role="button" label="Create expense"
# @post   role="button" label="Open actions menu"
# @tag    iou
# @tag    perf
# @tag    sentry-ManualCreateExpenseSubmit
# @tag    sentry-ManualSubmitToDestinationVisible
# @tag    sentry-ManualCreateExpenseServerResponse
# @tag    sentry-ManualGeolocationWait
press "role=\"button\" label=\"Create expense\" || label=\"Create expense\""
